      "comment": "HOOKED ON JOY (1) was last seen getting around 400m at this track in a decent 22.91 for a nose victory. In winning form and can measure up again. SUPER STORM (2) was below best last time at this track (23.64) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths sixth. Has already won out of this draw. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. BROADWAY KING (3) failed to come into contention last start at this track, but prior to that won by a nose at this track (23.01) beating Let's Trot Vixen in a Grade 5 on February 21. One of the better hopes. I'M ALRIGHT (7) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
